    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project or a source of parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including several large dents, deep scratches, and noticeable rust on the wheel arches and lower door panels. Mechanically, the engine requires a major overhaul, the transmission shifts roughly, and the interior upholstery is heavily worn and stained. It is currently not in reliable running condition and will need a fair amount of work to be roadworthy again.",
